{"id":10771,"date":"2024-03-17T15:02:51","date_gmt":"2024-03-17T08:02:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10771"},"modified":"2024-03-17T15:31:53","modified_gmt":"2024-03-17T08:31:53","slug":"dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec? H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh chi ti\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. V\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m <\/span><b>di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec? <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f9ng<\/span> <a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u201cDi\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y\u201d l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi hai t\u1eeb H\u00e1n &#8211; Vi\u1ec7t. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u201cth\u00f4ng\u201d c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng su\u1ed1t, tr\u00f4i ch\u1ea3y, c\u00f2n \u201cth\u1ee7y\u201d l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y gh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea3y qua m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf, t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn. Thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u trong b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong m\u1ea3ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10774\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10774\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10774 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10774\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10774\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10774\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o d\u1ef1a theo kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan t\u1ecfa<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o d\u1ef1a theo kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan t\u1ecfa, v\u1eabn hay g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cdi\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u201d, bao g\u1ed3m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch logia v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9, s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t hay h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt n\u1eb1m trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y (trong ti\u1ebfng anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 carpet), th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao ph\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Mu\u0323c \u0111i\u0301ch cu\u0309a vi\u00ea\u0323c xa\u0301c \u0111i\u0323nh di\u00ea\u0323n ti\u0301ch th\u00f4ng thuy\u0309<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khi mua nh\u00e0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 hay di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y n\u00ean g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10772\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10772\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10772 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10772\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10772\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y gi\u00fap x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, khi mua nh\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n trong gi\u1ea5y mua b\u00e1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y hay di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn hai th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 hay ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u1edbn, r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch, ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 di\u00ea\u0323n ti\u0301ch th\u00f4ng thuy\u0309 theo ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo Kho\u1ea3n 2, \u0110i\u1ec1u 101 Lu\u1eadt Nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2014 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u201c2. Ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1edf h\u1eefu ri\u00eang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y. Bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng b\u00ean trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9, logia, ban c\u00f4ng (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3). Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00e1c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e2n chia c\u0103n h\u1ed9, t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh nh\u00e0, h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t. V\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ban c\u00f4ng, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1eddng chung, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o t\u1eeb m\u00e9p trong c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1eddng chung.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9, t\u1ea1i \u0110i\u1ec1u 1, \u201cdi\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u201cDi\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u201d l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua b\u00e1n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o \u0111\u1ea1c d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y trong Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn c\u1ea5p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua. N\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u00f4 gia, ban c\u00f4ng (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3), li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1eddng chia gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t, t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt n\u1eb1m b\u00ean trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u2026\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10777\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10777\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10777 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10777\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10777\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10777\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh theo Kho\u1ea3n 2, \u0110i\u1ec1u 101 Lu\u1eadt Nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2014<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn v\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 trong Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 03\/2014\/TT &#8211; BXD, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 15\/8\/2016 v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 19\/2016\/TT &#8211; BXD v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 30\/6\/2016.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10773\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10773\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10773 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10773\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10773\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10773\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 19\/2016\/TT &#8211; BXD<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 03\/2014\/TT &#8211; BXD ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u201c&#8230;Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o \u0111\u1ea1c theo k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn c\u1ea5p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua, bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ban c\u00f4ng, logia (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u01b0\u1eddng chia gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t, h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9, t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh c\u0103n nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ban c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c t\u00ednh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n, n\u1ebfu ban c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng chung th\u00ec t\u00ednh lu\u00f4n t\u1eeb m\u00e9p trong c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1eddng chung. Khi giao quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9, \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u1ea7n ghi r\u00f5 trong bi\u00ean b\u1ea3n b\u00e0n giao c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c trong ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 b\u00e0n giao. Bi\u00ean b\u1ea3n b\u00e0n giao v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi nhau kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1ch r\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9 bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n gi\u1eefa m\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ban c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c logia c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u1eddng chia c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9, t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t, h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10778\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10778\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10778 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10778\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10778\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10778\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y bao g\u1ed3m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n h\u1ed9, v\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n, ban c\u00f4ng, logia,&#8230;<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 03\/2014\/TT &#8211; BXD tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng t\u01b0, trong \u0111\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">a, b: chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i, chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">c, d: chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng, chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a ban c\u00f4ng\/l\u00f4 gia (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">ei: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">f: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u00f9y v\u00e0o c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c nhau m\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt, h\u00ecnh tr\u00f2n, h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng,&#8230;t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ri\u00eang l\u1ebb t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia trong ng\u00e0nh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho gia ch\u1ee7 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1ec1 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed cho d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua khi bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi mua nh\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111o \u0111\u1ebfm v\u00e0 t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i cho m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua m\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi t\u00ednh to\u00e1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 \u0111o c\u1ee7a k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng kh\u1edbp v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. N\u1ebfu ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch di\u1ec7n t\u00edch trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u1edbn th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>B\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0103n h\u1ed9, n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh t\u1eeb m\u00e9p trong c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u1eddng thay v\u00ec t\u00ednh \u1edf tim t\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 chi tr\u1ea3 cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10775\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10775\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10775 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10775\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10775\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10775\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 c\u0103n h\u1ed9<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0, gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Nh\u00e0 2014 t\u1ea1i \u0110i\u1ec1u 106 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u1eebng t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c trao \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i m\u00e9t vu\u00f4ng (m2) di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 (ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y), theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Kho\u1ea3n 2, \u0110i\u1ec1u 30 t\u1ea1i Th\u00f4ng t\u01b0 02\/2016\/TT &#8211; BXD).<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Kinh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gia ch\u1ee7 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chung c\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3ng kinh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 (g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n giao c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a chung c\u01b0 m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng) m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10776\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10776\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10776 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10776\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10776\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10776\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kinh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh b\u1eb1ng gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh x di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kinh ph\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh x di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh kinh ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n, thu\u00ea mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 hay tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Chung quy l\u1ea1i, khi t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 theo k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch khi mua nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3ng kinh ph\u00ed v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh theo tim t\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ea3o th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd h\u00ecnh dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/dien-tich-thong-thuy-la-gi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><\/a><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i khi bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh to\u00e1n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y. H\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1e